      "comment": "COMPTON CHINOOK (1) rocketed out of the boxes with a scorching early sectional, clocking 22.72 in a 6 length win at this track over 400m. Safe beginner who draws ideally on the inside. Looks the testing material. LENNY LIMES (4) was prominent early from the tricky draw and did a fair job to be beaten half a length into second (19.91) at Angle Park in a Grade 6 over 342m. The form from his last run is stacking up nicely. Well placed and gets his chance. SHOOT THE BREEZE (3) stuck on well last time to finish 2 lengths back in second (22.95) at this track in a Other over 400m. Winning chance. TRADING HALT (2) can finish much closer after missing a cheque at this track last start.",
